'''Tower 78''' was one of many spires erupting out of the massive pyramid known as the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

==History==
A part of the Imperial Palace complex during the rule of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], Tower 78. Containing several [[Hangar/Legends|hangars]], chambers and over 400 levels, the Tower was the location of a meeting between [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] and [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] in the days following the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|battle]] above [[Yavin Prime/Legends|Yavin Prime]]. [[6 ABY/Legends|Several years]] after the death of both Vader and the Emperor, the Imperial [[Kirtan Loor]] was taken to level 443, bay 2, to meet with [[Director of Imperial Intelligence]] [[Ysanne Isard]].<ref name="XWRS" />

